{"type": "article", "id": 10394, "title": "Ace Hotel x Tokyobike 自行车系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-04T07:30:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606141042L47TQSqgjkp2FKuC.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\">时尚旅馆 Ace Hotel 和日本自行车品牌 Tokyobike 最近联手推出了一个自行车系列，此前他们曾经合作为 Ace Hotel 推出租赁款式，供住客租借。此次他们在之前款式的基础上进行了调整，变成了一个买走的自行车。这个系列中所由自行车配色都轻松明快，充满浓浓夏日风情，就像是加州的阳光和欧洲色缤纷色彩。目前自行车售价 875 美元，在洛杉矶和伦敦的 Ace Hotel 都可以买到，<a href=\"http://shop.acehotel.com/products/tokyobike\" target=\"_blank\">这是线上购买链接</a>。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141040X15kiFuCR7KNeQ8Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061410411E7OLhJFU2W5enTq.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141041ukLiSmX1QxPrsFJ4.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img sr